                    "line_text": "Tes yeux veillent sur la justice ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Sous tes pieds tombe l'artifice,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Par la main du Temps abattu :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Témoin sacré, juge inflexible,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Tu mis ton trône incorruptible",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Entre l'audace et la vertu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vérité, c'est toi que j'implore ;\nSoutiens ma voix, dicte mes vers.\nC'est toi qu'on craint et qu'on adore,\nToi qui fais trembler les pervers.\nTes yeux veillent sur la justice ;\nSous tes pieds tombe l'artifice,\nPar la main du Temps abattu :\nTémoin sacré, juge inflexible,\nTu mis ton trône incorruptible\nEntre l'audace et la vertu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Qu'un autre en sa fougue hautaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Insultant aux travaux de Mars,",
